              * The following commands display best case worst  case  derating
                factors:

                set_timing_derate  -cell_delay  -clock  -late  1.2  [get_cells
                {f2}] -min

                set_timing_derate -cell_delay -late 1.3 [get_cells {f2}] -max

                report_timing_derate

